-- Australia's Wotif bids for Travel.com
-- 
-- Sun Sep 30, 2007 8:20pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/10/01/us-travelcom-wotif-idUSSYU00319020071001

 

 SYDNEY  (Reuters) - Australia's Wotif.com Holdings Ltd ( WTF.AX ) said on Monday it planned to make a takeover offer for online travel agency Travel.com.au Ltd TVL.AX. 

 Wotif.com said in a statement it would offer 50 cents cash or a scrip alternative of between 0.0893 and 0.1042 of its own shares for each Travel.com share. The cash offer values Travel.com.au at A$49.8 million ($44 million).